Hey, look who's here.

14:18.558 --> 14:20.527
The school called
my parents today.

14:20.560 --> 14:21.794
Look, I had nothing
to do with that, okay?

14:23.530 --> 14:25.265
You gonna do this here?

14:26.533 --> 14:27.834
In front of everyone?

14:27.867 --> 14:29.836
Yeah, I guess you're
right, Strucker.

14:29.869 --> 14:32.205
This isn't the place.

14:32.239 --> 14:34.407
No...
This is the place.

14:34.441 --> 14:35.675
Wait, no, no!

14:35.708 --> 14:38.411
* So, baby, tell me yes

14:38.445 --> 14:39.712
* And I will be all...

