Let me go!

14:41.714 --> 14:44.617
Help! Help me!
(grunts)

14:44.651 --> 14:46.019
(grunts)

14:46.053 --> 14:49.056
Hey! Hey!
(grunts)

14:49.089 --> 14:50.190
Hey, Strucker.

14:50.223 --> 14:53.293
When was the last time
you took a shower?

14:53.326 --> 14:55.295
No, no, no... Aah! Aah!

14:55.328 --> 14:56.896
Sorry, man.
Too cold?

14:56.930 --> 14:58.598
Let me fix that.
(groans)

14:58.631 --> 15:01.434
How about... now?

15:01.468 --> 15:03.303
(shouting)
Is that warm enough for you?

15:03.336 --> 15:06.006
